Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.87,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}现在的你 全力支持着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.62,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在的我 也有了支持你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:29.63,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使彷徨无助 我们也要结伴前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.76,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}奔向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.77,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然与朋友们嬉戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}这样一路走来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:47.52,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却依然感到内心的空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.69,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受尽冷漠的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:54.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}寄身于时代的狂风中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:01:03.50,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}勇气与不安 如影相随
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:11.38,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}因此 现在就要用我的双手创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.55,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}那些让我们受伤感到绝望的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:21.89,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些令我们哭泣感到难过的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:23.85,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然萦绕于心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:27.86,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们终将跨过重重障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:32.11,CH_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}以超越所有人为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.87,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}君が今僕を支えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.62,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が今君を支える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:29.63,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから迷いながらも共に生きていこうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.76,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.77,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲間と戯れ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,250)}それなりで居ても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:47.52,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もの足りなさを感じてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:49.69,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷めた目で見られて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:54.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}乾いた時代の風に吹かれている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:01:03.50,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,400)}不安な心と勇気が背中合わせになっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:11.38,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}だけど今なら夢をこの手で叶えてみせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.55,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}傷ついて壊れそうな日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:21.89,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙して困らせる日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:23.85,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:27.86,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕達はそれを越えていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:32.11,JP_OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(000,600)}誰より上を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:46.47,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在哪里呢？{\fad(300,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.30,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我的宝藏{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:56.35,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在即将展开大冒险{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.01,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔和的阳光{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.03,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带给我启程的预感{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:06.28,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 天空和花朵都在向我微笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.02,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前方等待我的将是什么呢？{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.12,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:18.92,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻开启梦想之门…{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.29,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「  走吧！」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.63,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使狂风吹袭{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.30,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使内心动摇{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.01,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使手中握着的是空白的地图{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.80,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使狂风吹袭{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.68,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要描绘美好的明天{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:38.31,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着远方  去往何方？ 直到那最终的彼方{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.27,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不言败{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.06,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不哭泣{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:46.82,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到梦想成真的那一天{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.93,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空在微笑{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.57,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花儿也在微笑{\fad(100,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:54.45,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我也一定会开怀大笑{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:58.96,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何艰难险阻都能跨越{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:04.25,CH_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也 再也…不会害怕了{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:46.47,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこにあるのかな{\fad(300,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.30,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクだけの宝物{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:56.35,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今 大きな冒険へ{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.01,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やわらかな日差し{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:02.03,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅立ちの予感{\fad(100,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:06.28,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空も花も ホラ 笑っている{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:11.02,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この先には何が待つのだろう？{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.12,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:18.92,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢の扉にそっと手をかけて…{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.29,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「  行こう！」{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.63,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に吹かれながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.30,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心揺らしながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:30.01,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真っ白な地図を片手に持ちながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.80,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風に吹かれながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.68,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日を描きながら{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:38.31,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠くまで 何処まで？ たどり着けるまで{\fad(200,100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.27,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対負けないよ{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.06,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶対泣かないよ{\fad(500,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:46.82,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この夢を叶えるその日までは{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.93,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの空は笑っていた{\fad(300,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.57,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの花は笑っていた{\fad(100,300)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:54.45,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクもいつか笑うから{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:58.96,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな壁も越えるから{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:04.25,JP_ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう 何も 何も…コワクナイ{\fad(200,700)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【注释】
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到在濑户海的因岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:02.29,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因岛：濑户内海诸岛之一 位于广岛东南部\n是本因坊秀策的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17·四 右上角 「小目」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:32.74,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小目」：四个星位周围靠近角的两个位置就是小目 棋盘中共有8个小目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「尖」?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.93,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「尖」：围棋中在己方原有棋子的斜上或斜下一路处行棋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他用的是很古老的定式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:16:01.76,reference,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「定式」：围棋活动中长久以来逐渐形成的各种进攻或防守的模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【对白】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这既不是最好的一手 也不是最强的一手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45}{\fnsimhei}{\bord2}{\i1}{\3c&H000000&}{\pos(425,365)}永远的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑快点 小明 马上就到爷爷家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说嘛 直接回家不就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这样好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么都是些没用的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 我们走吧 这里好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自这么做真的可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上次的社会课考试我只考了8分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以零用钱都被扣掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 这个好像不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我知道 是下五子棋的棋盘对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爷爷以前用过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许可以卖个好价钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做真的可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.94,0:03:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 没事 爷爷一定是忘掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把上面的灰尘擦掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个污迹怎么也擦不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什么污迹啊 很干净啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有啊 哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我刚刚不是说在这里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以听到我的声音吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以听到我的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实没有什么污迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 小光 不要说吓人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爷爷吗? 快出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所不能的神明啊  万分感激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在又再度回到这个世界上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 小光 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 小光出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原佐为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为 你是什么人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是平安时代在皇宫内教天皇下围棋的棋师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天 每天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一盘 一盘 能够一直下棋 我感到很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 除了我以外  还有个棋师在教天皇下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天 他向天皇进言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说棋师一个就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下让我们通过对局一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获胜的一方才能继续留下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他决斗了?谁赢了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋盘上的战斗进行得难分难解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正当大家都凝神于棋局上的时侯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我在无意间发现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的棋盒里竟然混有一个白棋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把那个白子放在自己的胜子里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作弊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正想说出来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是不是把\n我的黑子放进了你自己的胜子里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的伎俩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是什么无聊的藉口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趁大家注意棋局的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:06:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事先混在\n棋盒里的黑子放到你的胜子里 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是那样做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丢脸了 都给朕安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种下流的手段会在朕的面前发生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕连想都没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我输了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我无法抑制心中的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着作弊的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被赶出了皇宫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法再生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天之后 我投水自尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我还想…还想再下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}我的灵魂无法安息 便附在了那个棋盘上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过了很长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了一个少年的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫 虎次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.09,0:07:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你可以看到我怨恨的泪水的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我留在你的心里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎次郎改名为秀策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20岁就成为师傅的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并最终成为14世本因坊秀策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本因坊秀策?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 他却被一种流行病打垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一晚 年仅34岁的他就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋盘上的血迹就是他留下的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 你就附在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是为了想继续下棋吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:08:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我还没有领悟到「神之一手」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 听说你昨天被救护车拉走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 你真的没事吗? 昨天怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我自己也记不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒来的时候已经今天早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家往后传
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是历史题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没… 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来 继续考试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的事原来不是做梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字叫什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的那么喜欢下棋?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想继续下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对下棋可是一点兴趣都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么? 混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做 什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤 没事吧? 要不要去保健室?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是我不能下棋的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渗入到了你的意识里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了你那执着了千年的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我有我自己的人生目标哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我以外就不能找别人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:09:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔下下也没什么问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的心还是我自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…到底是谁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有10分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完的同学再检查一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为 你知道吗? 天保变革
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天保? 是水野大人发起的那次变革吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好怀念哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经和他在屋内对弈过一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那佩里你认识吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩里?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩里 就是乘坐钢铁战舰来的那个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佩里提督吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那个佩里提督是在哪儿登陆的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦贺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时还引起很大的轰动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦贺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤 你在自言自语些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考题做完了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一会儿就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过人家身体的时候也不道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 这个时代的女性真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就不要在我脑袋里面吵了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考完试以后就带你去下棋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好多人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为东京是大城市嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 还有 我们要去哪里下棋呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围棋会场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷有时候也会去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是很多喜欢下棋的老伯聚集的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么时代 总有人喜欢下棋的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6}{\pos(295,298)\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs15\3c&HDA644B&\be1}平日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6}{\pos(265,342)\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs15\3c&HDA644B&\be1}周六日 节假日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz1}{\pos(340,111)\fs20\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\3c&H400000&}skyblue travel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz1}{\pos(340,141)}{\fs16\bord0\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1}{\c&H404000&}各种旅游 租赁业务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-1\pos(413,210)\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs24\bord2\b1\3c&HEC2F6F&}紫水围棋沙龙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安 请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 都是些老头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一次来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是来这里 什么都是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁下都可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在这里写下你的名字 棋力是多少?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋力?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没和人对弈过 我想我应该很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有小孩吗? 我可以和他下吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以 但是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找对弈的对手吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 我和你下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到里面下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小孩子要交500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要交钱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他第一次来这儿 就免费招待他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小亮这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫塔矢亮 你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进藤光 小学6年级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是6年级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对手是老头就没有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的棋力怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.42,0:13:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但应该很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚却又很厉害?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就先让你4到5子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让子? 你要让我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦 我们年龄差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟塔矢亮下还不用让子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不知天高地厚的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你先下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能下得很慢 请多多见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐为 你真的那么高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔了140年这么久…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小光 要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17·…1、2、3、4
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他拿子的姿势完全像个新手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·十七 右下角 「小目」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·十七 这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3·十六
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3·十六
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16·五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14·四
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14·四
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然拿棋的方式像是初学者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是下的棋路却很稳健
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如他自己说的 很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 快点下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且为什么他常常会在奇怪的地方停下来?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14·十一 这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他毫不理会我的进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 与其说是不理会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是轻松化解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个白子是你的了 拿下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19·十五
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拿走了可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18·十四
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可以拿下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那9个白子已经被逼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些白子都会成为你的胜子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很轻松嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 对方也不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些子不是我要拿的 是他不要的弃子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我左上角的9子被逼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我还可以控制住中央部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4·十三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8·五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 8·五  是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这既不是最好的一手 也不是最强的一手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在试探我接下去该怎么走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在观察我的棋力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很高的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:18:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.94,0:19:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下完了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 果然对弈对我来说还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下了那么长的时间 好累哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有个儿童围棋比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得再来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要和小亮对弈再过50年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了!? 怎么可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮输了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮的实力可是接近职业水平的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让子了吧? 让了几子?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是执黑先行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了几目?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果算上5目半贴目的话应该是小亮赢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2目之差吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是一个等级
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小亮输了是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那孩子说他从没和别人下过棋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从…没和…别人…下过棋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不习惯的事做起来果然很累
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你满足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 回家写社会课的作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 跑着回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【GoGo】
